citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
An authorized adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15 am on
4/22/24. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee by knocking on the door and calling his cell phone. His wife
answered the door and stated that he was not home and she was unable to conduct the inspection. Failure to provide
access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to
comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
An authorized adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15 am on 
4/22/24. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee by knocking on the door and calling his cell phone. His wife 
answered the door and stated that he was not home and she was unable to conduct the inspection. Failure to provide 
access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to 
comply may result in enforcement action. 
 
 
End Section
